power in the Particle Thrower and Overclocking your weapon! Or maybe you just wanna push stuff around? Don't worry there's an ability for that.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">A variety of ships means you can start your build where you want: Need a slow ship with a lot of firepower? Got you covered with the Vulture. Wanna be &quot;fast as f*@k boi?&quot; Go for the Sparrow. Wanna spam that ability? Look no further than the Owl.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Then jump in and survive hordes of hostile Shapes, each one mechanically distinct and requiring a different approach to defeat.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/tri.png?t=1732582248\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/791516c7-d05c-405c-9f96-4907e8f5864e.png?t=1732582248\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/squer.png?t=1732582248\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/53e475e3-43d1-4d36-a3ba-bcb28282b978.png?t=1732582248\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/29a816ee-e56a-4001-bbf3-5ecf9a01bf04.png?t=1732582248\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/7b50a0c8-de28-4d2b-a5fd-ce5d3d1b4911.png?t=1732582248\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/extras/accf756a-0171-4971-b4bb-4f9a5296f38c.png?t=1732582248\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">As you kill more and more Shapes, level up and upgrade your ship in a myriad of ways and unlock Unique Perks which can drastically alter how your Ship plays.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore colorful galaxies and conquer cataclysmic events like Asteroid Fields and Solar Winds as you navigate the disintegration of the Universe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Don't Die. Kill Shapes. Shapes-Like.</p>","developers":["natureboyian"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Casual","id":"4"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3359520/header.jpg?t=1732582248","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257076106,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076106/movie480.mp4?t=1732582241","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076106/movie_max.mp4?t=1732582241"},"name":"Steam Announcement Teaser","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257076106/c101a8926544b7fb954ddb023e119b63f411580b/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1732582241","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076106/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1732582241","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257076106/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1732582241"}}],"name":"Shapes-Like","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS:</strong> Windows 10<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</strong> Quad-Core<br></li><li><strong>Memory:</strong> 4 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Graphics:</strong> 2 GB RAM<br></li><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 100 MB available space</li></ul>"},"platforms":{"linux":false,"mac":false,"windows":true},"publishers":["natureboyian"],"ratings":{"dejus":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Viol\u00eancia","rating":"10","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"10","use_age_gate":"0"},"steam_germany":{"banned":"0","descriptors":"Gewalt","rating":"12","rating_generated":"1","required_age":"12","use_age_gate":"0"}},"release_date":{"coming_soon":true,"date":"To be announced"},"required_age":0,"screenshots":[{"id":0,"path_full":"https://shared.akamai.